  "help.documents_items": "Upload document: click 'Upload Document' and select project, category and file.|Available categories: Blueprint, Technical Specification, Contract, Procedure, Permit, Report, Minutes, Budget, Schedule.|Accepted formats: PDF, DWG, DXF, DOC/DOCX, XLS/XLSX, PPT/PPTX, JPG/PNG, ZIP/RAR (max. 50MB).|Download: click the download icon to get the file.|Filter: use project and category filters to find specific documents.|Versions: indicate the document version for traceability.|From the project detail, the 'Documents' tab shows only that project's documents.",

