  "help.dashboard_desc": "Main panel with key performance indicators (KPIs).",
  "help.dashboard_items": "Shows total inspections and this month's count.|Indicates open, critical and overdue observations.|Displays overall project compliance rate.|Includes charts for inspections by week and observations by severity.|Contractor ranking shows compliance levels.",

  "help.companies_title": "Companies",
  "help.companies_desc": "Manage client and contractor companies registered in the system.",
  "help.companies_items": "Create company: click 'New Company' and enter Tax ID, business name, contact info and address.|Edit company: click the pencil icon on the corresponding row.|Delete company: click the trash icon (only if no associated projects).|Company types: Client (project owner) or Contractor (executes the work).|Use the search bar to filter by name, Tax ID or type.",

  "help.projects_title": "Projects",
  "help.projects_desc": "Manage construction projects associated with companies.",
  "help.projects_items": "Create project: click 'New Project' and fill in code, name, company, type and dates.|View detail: click on the project code or name.|Structure: from the detail you can manage stages, sectors and units.|Members: assign users to the project with specific roles (Director, Supervisor, Inspector).|Statuses: Planning, In Progress, Paused, Finished.|Use the search bar to filter by code, name or status.",

  "help.project_detail_title": "Project Detail",
  "help.project_detail_desc": "Complete view of a project with all its information and structure.",
  "help.project_detail_items": "General info: shows code, company, type, status, dates and location.|Structure: manage Stages > Sectors > Units of the project.|Members: add or remove users assigned to the project.|Edit: modify project data with the 'Edit' button.|Delete: only if no associated inspections or observations.",

  "help.inspections_title": "Inspections",
  "help.inspections_desc": "Manage technical construction inspections.",
  "help.inspections_items": "Create inspection: click 'New Inspection' and select project, template, inspector and date.|View detail: click on the inspection code.|Statuses: Scheduled, In Progress, Completed, Cancelled.|Score: automatically calculated based on conforming vs non-conforming answers.|Result: Passed (score >= template threshold) or Failed.|Start inspection: changes status to 'In Progress' to begin recording answers.|Complete: finish the inspection when all questions are answered.",

  "help.inspection_detail_title": "Inspection Detail",
  "help.inspection_detail_desc": "Complete view of an inspection with its sections and answers.",
  "help.inspection_detail_items": "General data: project, inspector, template, status, score and result.|Answers: each section shows questions with conformity (Conforming, Non-Conforming, N/A).|Critical questions: marked with a star, significantly affect the score.|Notes: each answer can have additional notes.|Actions: start, complete or cancel the inspection based on its current status.",

  "help.observations_title": "Observations / Non-Conformities",
  "help.observations_desc": "Record and manage observations detected during inspections.",
  "help.observations_items": "Create observation: click 'New Observation' and fill in project, title, severity and description.|View detail: click on the observation code.|Severity: Low, Medium, High, Critical. Critical ones require immediate attention.|Statuses: Open, In Progress, Resolved, Closed.|Due date: indicates the resolution deadline. Overdue ones are highlighted in red.|Close observation: from the detail, add a closing comment.|Use filters to view observations by status, severity or project.",

  "help.observation_detail_title": "Observation Detail",
  "help.observation_detail_desc": "Complete view of an observation with all its information.",
  "help.observation_detail_items": "Information: project, severity, status, contractor, responsible person and dates.|Description: complete detail of the detected observation.|Location: description of where the observation was detected.|Close: click 'Close Observation' and add a resolution comment.|Edit: modify observation data while it is open.",

  "help.templates_title": "Inspection Templates",
  "help.templates_desc": "Define templates with sections and questions for inspections.",
  "help.templates_items": "Create template: click 'New Template' and enter name, type and description.|View detail: click on the template name.|Sections: group questions by topics (e.g.: Structure, Installations, Safety).|Questions: each section contains questions to be answered during the inspection.|Critical questions: mark as critical if a 'Non-Conforming' should significantly affect the result.|Statuses: Draft (editable), Published (ready to use), Archived.",

  "help.template_detail_title": "Template Detail",
  "help.template_detail_desc": "View and edit sections and questions of a template.",
  "help.template_detail_items": "Add section: click 'Add Section' and enter the title.|Add question: within each section, add questions with text and answer type.|Sort: sections and questions are shown in the defined order.|Delete: you can delete questions or sections (their questions are also deleted).|Only templates in Draft status can be edited.",

  "help.users_title": "Users",
  "help.users_desc": "Manage platform users and their roles.",
  "help.users_items": "Create user: click 'New User' and enter name, email, Tax ID and role.|Available roles: SuperAdmin, AdminTenant, Director, Supervisor, Inspector.|SuperAdmin: full system access.|AdminTenant: manages their company and projects.|Director: manages projects and assigns inspectors.|Supervisor: oversees inspections and observations.|Inspector: performs inspections and records observations.|Edit: modify user data with the pencil icon.|Deactivate: deactivate a user without removing them from the system.",

  "help.specialties_title": "Specialties",
  "help.specialties_desc": "Define technical specialties available for classifying inspections.",
  "help.specialties_items": "Create specialty: click 'New Specialty' and enter name, code and color.|Examples: Structural Work, Finishing, Electrical Installations, Plumbing.|Color: allows visual identification of the specialty in lists and reports.|Edit or delete: use the action icons on each row.|Specialties are used when classifying inspections and templates.",

  "help.contractors_title": "Contractors",
  "help.contractors_desc": "Manage contractors that execute construction works.",
  "help.contractors_items": "Create contractor: click 'New Contractor' and enter name, Tax ID and contact details.|Associated company: link the contractor to a registered company.|Contact: record name, email and phone of the responsible person.|Edit or delete: use the action icons on each row.|Contractors are assigned to inspections and observations.",

  "help.reports_title": "Reports",
  "help.reports_desc": "Generate PDF and Excel reports from system data.",
  "help.reports_items": "Inspection PDF Report: select project and inspection, then click 'Download PDF'.|The PDF includes general data, score, result and detail of all answers.|Observations Excel Report: select a project and download the complete list.|The Excel includes code, title, severity, status, due date and statistical summary.|Reports are downloaded directly to the browser.",

  "help.general_title": "General Help — ITO Cloud",
  "help.general_desc": "Technical Works Inspection Platform for managing projects, inspections and observations.",
  "help.general_items": "Navigation: use the side menu to access the different modules.|Dashboard: general view with KPIs and charts.|Projects: manage construction projects, structure and members.|Inspections: schedule and execute technical inspections with templates.|Observations: record non-conformities and track them until closure.|Templates: define questions and sections for inspections.|Reports: generate PDFs of inspections and Excel of observations.|Users: manage accounts and access roles.|Click the help button (?) on each module for specific help."
}
